      "option": 2,
      "citation": "Communion Antiphon • Option I | Cf. Ps 31 (30):17–18",
      "text": "Let your face shine on your servant.\nSave me in your merciful love.\nO Lord, let me never be put to shame, for I call on you."
    }
  ],
